## 🔧 Problems Solved

| Problem | Cause | Solution |
|---------|-------|----------|
| `pip install` failed | ChromaDB required `fastapi==0.115.9`, we pinned `0.115.12` | Changed from exact versions (`==`) to minimum versions (`>=`) |
| FastAPI couldn't connect to PostgreSQL | Local PostgreSQL on port 5432 conflicted with Docker | Changed Docker to port **5433** |
| Docker wouldn't start | Docker Desktop wasn't running | Launched Docker Desktop first |

